Interface AiHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TridentAiHandler

    public interface AiHandler
    Handles the assigning of AIs to Entities on the server.
    Since:
    0.3-alpha-DP
    Author:
    The TridentSDK Team

    • Method Detail

      • defaultAiFor

        AiModule defaultAiFor(EntityType type)
        Returns the AI Module that is the default for a certain type of entity

      • setDefaultAiFor

        void setDefaultAiFor(EntityType type,
                     AiModule module)
        Sets the AI for this entity type, used to provide a separate AiModule for Entities

        Entities of this type in the world will immediately start using this AiModule, even if they were created before this was set.

        Parameters:
        type - the type of entity to replace the AI for
        module - the new AiModule to use

      • nativeAIFor

        AiModule nativeAIFor(EntityType type)
        Returns the server's implementation of the AI for a given entity type
        Parameters:
        type - the type of entity to request the AI for
